data.description: Introducing a Timeless Treasure in the Heart of a Beloved Neighborhood that will come with a FREE home warranty! Step into your dream home with this enchanting family residence. Over the years, it has evolved into a masterpiece that seamlessly combines modern elegance with comfortable living. The heart of this home is its inviting kitchen, where you'll find culinary inspiration at every turn. A recent-in-years renovation introduced pristine white cabinets, sleek granite countertops, and state-of-the-art appliances, offering the perfect space for your culinary adventures!  As you enter, be prepared to be captivated by the enchanting atmosphere. The upgraded dark floating laminate floors greet you with their captivating charm, setting the stage for the entire home. These floors are more than just a visual treat; they provide the perfect backdrop for your unique decorating style. This home is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance throughout. Large windows and thoughtful design choices ensure that every corner enjoys its fair share of sunshine. Whether it's the gentle morning glow or the golden hues of sunset, you'll always be surrounded by nature's beauty. Step outside into your private haven – a fenced-in backyard that offers safety for your beloved pets and little ones. It's a sanctuary where family gatherings, barbecues, and starlit evenings become cherished memories.  HVAC and water heater were recently replaced, ensuring your comfort and peace of mind. Enjoy cozy evenings by the natural wood fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxation. Exciting news: The roof is scheduled for replacement, adding to the list of improvements that make this home even more desirable.  It's time to transform this beautiful house into your forever home. Be sure to call your preferred agent today and schedule your showing! All descriptions/dimensions are believed to be accurate but must be verified by buyer(s) if deemed to be important.
